8n/T%C3%A2y-%C4%91%C3%ACnh/poem-IvSySNKhFxfiI1JFeEaNuQ">Tây đình - 西亭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/Tu%C3%BD-hoa-%C3%A2m/poem-TX3A1SievQzdSQcY5LnHww">Tuý hoa âm - 醉花陰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/Uy%E1%BB%83n-chuy%E1%BB%83n-ca/poem-Pa4QTIR4hftfyjMW83pTqQ">Uyển chuyển ca - 宛轉歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADn/author-eBGdtm3O4c2NQ7sIhikeXg">Dương Thận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Xu%C3%A2n-khu%C3%AA/poem-QO38f6KlSNkYYZMUIJ596A">Xuân khuê - 春閨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
